    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Ballot
    A Ballot contains the ranking that a single voter gave to the candidates on the ballot.
    Candidate
    A Candidate represents a person who is running for office.
    Election
    An Election consists of the candidates running for office, the ballots that have been cast, and the total number of voters.
    RankedChoiceVoting
    The ranked choice voting program implements the ranked choice voting algorithm.
